            (act): Silu()

  )

      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )

        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

      (2): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()

      (0): Conv2D(128, 4, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      (2): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )
)

    )

    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()

  )

            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n4): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

            (act): Silu()
          )

            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (head): YOLOXHead(
    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      )

      )
    )

      (0): BaseConv(

      )

      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv2): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n3): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

          )
        )
      )
    )

      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

        (conv): Conv2D(256, 64, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv2): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n3): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )

      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

      (act): Silu()
    )

          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (head): YOLOXHead(
    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      )

        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_convs): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (reg_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 4, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      (0): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )

            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv2): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n3): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )

      (conv1): BaseConv(

  )

    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )

        (act): Silu()
      )

            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n4): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 512, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=512, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (head): YOLOXHead(
    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )
      (2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_convs): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

      )

      )
    )

      (0): BaseConv(

        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (reg_preds): Sequential(

    )

    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()

            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (head): YOLOXHead(
    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_convs): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )

        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

      )

      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (reg_preds): Sequential(

    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )

        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)

          )
        )
      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )
)

            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)

          )
        )
      )
    )

      )

    (cls_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )
)

    )

    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()

    (obj_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )
)

            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv2): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n3): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n4): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

          )

  )
  (head): YOLOXHead(
    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)

      )

      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_convs): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

      )

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (reg_preds): Sequential(

      (1): Conv2D(128, 4, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

    (obj_preds): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (1): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (2): Conv2D(128, 1, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
    )
    (l1_loss): L1Loss()
    (bcewithlog_loss): BCEWithLogitsLoss()
    (iou_loss): IOUloss()
  )

          )
        )
      )
    )
    (upsample): Upsample(scale_factor=2, mode=nearest, align_corners=False, align_mode=0, data_format=NCHW)
    (lateral_conv0): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_p4): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (reduce_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_p3): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 64, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(

        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv2): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()

      (conv1): BaseConv(

        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)

      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

          )
        )
      )
    )

      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)

      (act): Silu()

        (conv): Conv2D(512, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)

        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(64, 64, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=64, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv2): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )

      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )

            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(

      )

      (1): Conv2D(128, 80, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n3): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
    (bu_conv1): BaseConv(
      (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], stride=[2, 2], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
      (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
      (act): Silu()
    )
    (C3_n4): CSPLayer(
      (conv1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv2): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(512, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )
      (conv3): BaseConv(

        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=512, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (m): Sequential(
        (0): Bottleneck(
          (conv1): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
          (conv2): BaseConv(
            (conv): Conv2D(256, 256, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
            (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=256, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
            (act): Silu()
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
  (head): YOLOXHead(
    (stems): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(256, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

      )

        (conv): Conv2D(512, 128, kernel_size=[1, 1], data_format=NCHW)

        (act): Silu()
      )
    )
    (cls_convs): Sequential(
      (0): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
        (bn): BatchNorm2D(num_features=128, momentum=0.9, epsilon=1e-05)
        (act): Silu()
      )
      (1): BaseConv(
        (conv): Conv2D(128, 128, kernel_size=[3, 3], padding=1, data_format=NCHW)
